Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:40.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure that Brother\Nis somewhere, doing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:03.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:29.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous!\NBe careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:38.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're\Nmiddle school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:04.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!\NIt's our time to use the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:06.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reserved this time slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, you're a bunch of brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we're using this field!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:24.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use that empty area\Non the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:30.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's our time to use it!\NFollow the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:35.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bother...\NYou don't even need a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't get much time to use the field\Nbecause you brats reserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean\Nwe don't need the field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got practice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:46.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:47.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:53.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve!\NYou're just grade schoolers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:04:00.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if we're just grade schoolers!\NFollow the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:08.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An empty lot is good enough for kids!\NYou're not even serious about practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We are serious!\Nwe're far more serious than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even follow the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that poor players shouldn't\Neven bother making reservations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really better than we are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:24.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so confident,\Nshall we play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:35.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll play a game of soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not playing around,\Nthen show us your skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:44.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kurosaki, what are you saying?!\N- Kurosaki, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Let's accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll play here next Saturday evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, we're going to make you\Neat spaghetti through your noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:04.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you back out on us either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, what are we going to do?\NThat's quite an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:19.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose, we have to eat spaghetti\Nthrough our noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!\NWe just have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's show some spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is showing spirit enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to come up\Nwith some sort of strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we ask\Nyour brother to help us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother seems like\Nhe's good at sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Our opponents\Nare middle school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right if we get help from\Na high school student, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:02.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... My brother can't do it.\NHe's on a trip right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:11.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for someone else\Nwho's good at soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else? Who is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's that guy from this morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You picked up my ball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:50.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what school do you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:06:59.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't go to any school!\NI'm busy! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can play soccer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a soccer match!\Nwant to play with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:15.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at him...\NHe's got silver hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably colored it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he looks fierce.\NHe's probably a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:33.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring a guy like that\Non to our team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, is that little guy\Nreally good at soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a midget?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We never went as far\Nas to call you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:46.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Amazing!\N- Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's amazing!\N- That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro Hitsugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:36.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro, huh? What a cool name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you color your hair, Toshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hairstyle is pretty neat, Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! You're our only hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I told you, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just a regular Hollow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:57.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that sensation again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the only one nearby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:07.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Toshiro! Where're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got urgent business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I can't help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:15.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be practicing every day\Nat the park on the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to come tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We really can't get\Nmuch practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:35.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Toshiro didn't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:39.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that we'd\Ngotten a strong ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:44.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we should practice\Neating spaghetti through our noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Wait, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys keep practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew he'd be here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:24.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come to practice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:27.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that I'd help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't have the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a grade schooler.\NWhat are you so busy doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:40.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why do you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:41.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you listening, Toshiro?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:00.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cause I can see the sky\Nthe best from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told you to stop calling me "Toshiro"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll call you by your last name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when you've been admitted\Ninto the same place that I have!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who'd go there?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It brings back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brings back memories?\NHow old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:44.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:49.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... No... How should I put this?\NI sense something bad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that she...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:01.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone defeated it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:04.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... You'll come tomorrow, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:33.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stalking someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just something\NI'm curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interested in a girl\Nfrom the World of the Living?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now...\NYou don't need to be bashful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:51.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:55.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Toshiro never came...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:16.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody could get anyone\Nto help us, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should have practiced\Neating spaghetti through our noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should just apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:29.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far.\NWe've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you all!\NCome on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right...\N- All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- O-Okay!\N- O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Middle school students\Nsure are strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you getting timid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:50.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I told you that I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:57.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Everyone, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never made any promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going make\Nour counterattack now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting someone\Nto help them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we're going to\Nmake a comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right!\N- All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:39.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here to play soccer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:53.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well...\NWe just have to win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing players!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:10.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:39.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go!\N- Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:45.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your team...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- We did it!\N- We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- We did it! We did it!\N- We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:22.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Toshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:29.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You made the winning goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have to\Nask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's appeared again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a Huge Hollow...\NNo, is it a Menos?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:02.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:03.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro, you can see that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later. Anyway, run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:13.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:15.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stand by\Nwhile this happens to my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't affect him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:44.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The same black kimono\Nthat Brother has...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Soul Reaper...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Frost unto the Heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:08.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you.\NI'm in the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Cero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How is everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:42.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank goodness.\N- Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- What happened?\N- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That freaked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:50.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro, that uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you have\Nstrong spiritual power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never expected that\Nyou could see me in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you know\Nwhere my brother is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the way you're dressed,\Nyou're a Soul Reaper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know\Nabout Soul Reapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother is also a Soul Reaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:17.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're Ichigo Kurosaki's\Nyounger sister... That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:22.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:33.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki is trying to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what,\Nhe doesn't give up until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sort of person he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He's your brother right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:21:00.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a Soul Reaper, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:07.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You have subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:15.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Captain, this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Ichigo Kurosaki's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:19.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:24.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rangiku Matsumoto.\NI'm Captain Hitsugaya's Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. You really are a Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are cool, Toshiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:32.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're\Na grade schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A grade schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:39.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:43.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must you\Nmake the same mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a grade schooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:23.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, good work helping out\Nthose grade schoolers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:24.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:27.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:30.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Come to think of it, we're helping out\Nhigh school students next!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:31.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "next"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:33.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's give it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:34.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:37.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:39.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having okonomiyaki\Nfor dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:42.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all be gone if you don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:46.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:47.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:48.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:50.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to eat rice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:52.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked some rice! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:55.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why? We're having\Nokonomiyaki today, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:56.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:59.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat the okonomiyaki with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:02.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...it's a carbohydrate\Nwith a carbohydrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:03.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's essential!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:05.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!